sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client / ModelMesh Service
    participant Proxy as REST Proxy Server<br/>8008/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant ReqTx as Request Transformer<br/>(in-process)
    participant GRPCGw as gRPC-Gateway<br/>(in-process)
    participant ModelSrv as Model Server (localhost)<br/>8033/TCP gRPC

    Note over Client, ModelSrv: Flow 1: REST Inference Request

    Client->>Proxy: POST /v2/models/{name}/infer<br/>HTTP/HTTPS (Optional TLS)<br/>JSON Body: ModelInferRequest
    Proxy->>ReqTx: Decode JSON request
    Note over ReqTx: Flatten multi-dimensional tensors<br/>Decode base64 BYTES data<br/>Map tensor data types<br/>(BOOL, INT8-64, UINT8-64, FP32, FP64, BYTES)
    ReqTx->>GRPCGw: Protobuf ModelInferRequest
    GRPCGw->>ModelSrv: gRPC ModelInfer<br/>8033/TCP (Optional TLS)
    ModelSrv-->>GRPCGw: gRPC ModelInferResponse
    Note over GRPCGw: Convert protobuf response<br/>Encode BYTES as base64<br/>Format tensor outputs as JSON
    GRPCGw-->>Proxy: JSON ModelInferResponse
    Proxy-->>Client: HTTP 200 OK<br/>JSON Response

    Note over Client, ModelSrv: Flow 2: Model Metadata Request

    Client->>Proxy: GET /v2/models/{name}<br/>HTTP/HTTPS (Optional TLS)
    Proxy->>GRPCGw: Forward request
    GRPCGw->>ModelSrv: gRPC ModelMetadata<br/>8033/TCP (Optional TLS)
    ModelSrv-->>GRPCGw: gRPC ModelMetadataResponse
    GRPCGw-->>Proxy: JSON response
    Proxy-->>Client: HTTP 200 OK<br/>JSON ModelMetadata
